1. On je čovekom *čovek* od poverenja. (He is a man of trust.) 
2. Čovekom *čoveka* se čini da je lepši od ostalih. (It seems to the man that he is prettier than the others.) 
3. Čovekom *čoveku* je potrebno više vremena da stekne znanje. (A man needs more time to acquire knowledge.) 
4. Ona je uvek bila čovekom *čoveka* koji ne gubi vreme. (She has always been a man who doesn't waste time.) 
5. Čovekom *čoveke* je poznat po njegovom poštenju. (The man is known for his honesty.)